snippet.textDisplay:
All the people from Pakistan always must should many thanks to 'Coke Studio Pakistan' because they give a proper platform to Pakistani singing talents. As we always see, Pakistan has much better singing talent than India, no doubt about it. But regretfully from the starting Pakistani were always backward in print, electronics, and tv or satellite & in all kinds of media, so they did not get any rich platform to publish or to florish their talent, in this situation Coke Studio gives the right opportunity.

Syed Jamil Yousuf
Chittagong, Bangladesh.
